snippet.title: Johnny Depp with Fiancée Amber Heard leaving Jimmy Kimmel 2015
snippet.description: http://youtube.com/starpaptv Johnny Depp with girlfriend Amber Heard trying to hide from Fans on the streets of Hollywood. Promoting his new Movie on Jimmy Kimmel for Mordecai. They on their way to the 20th Critics' Choice Award in Hollywood California at the Palladium on Sunset Blvd. The 51-year-old actor dished on his fiancée in an interview with OK magazine as he said: "She's a strong, brilliant woman who has a lot to say. That combination is pretty devastating." Exclusive Video from Hollywood California from Behind the Scenes of Celebrity Life and Star Sightings. http://StarPapTV.com
tags: johnny depp at critics choice awards
